Does the project have a release methodology? Please document it in RELEASES.md.
Initially, we plan to release an initial framework in April, a revised one in the June to August timeframe, and roll out another release in September of 2024. 

Does the project have a code of conduct? If yes, please share the URL. If no, please created CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md and point to https://lfprojects.org/policies/code-of-conduct/. You can use conduct@lfai.foundation as email for contact on this topic.
Intel projects adopt the Contributor Covenant. After joining LF AI & Data, we will adopt the Linux Foundation CoC. 

